val seq = Seq("offerViewId")
val parquetFileOffer = sqlContext.read.parquet("/home/ama/sidana/calypso_purch_feb_march_data/*.parquet")
val groupedImpressions = parquetFileOffer.groupBy("userId").count.sort(desc("count"))
val groupedClicks = parquetFileOffer.filter(parquetFileOffer("wasClicked")).groupBy("userId").count.sort(desc("count"))
val groupedOffers = parquetFileOffer.dropDuplicates(seq).groupBy("userId").count.sort(desc("count"))
val impAvg = groupedImpressions.select(avg($"count"))
impAvg.show
val offerAvg = groupedOffers.select(avg($"count"))
offerAvg.show
val clickAvg = groupedClicks.select(avg($"count"))
clickAvg.show
